%@4@%%@AB@%Width table will need to be reentered%@AE@%%@EH@%%@NL@%

This is another warning that changing your character range invalidates your
width table.  %@NL@%


%@4@%%@AB@%Write over original %@AB@%filename?%@AE@%%@AE@%%@EH@%%@NL@%

